{"tid":1970702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰網紅自稱「台灣女孩」被屈台獨","createTime":"2020-04-13T10:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T08:49:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58c020c10817e44abee4d6eb9764f3eb7c047819","tid":1970702,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200413/5S3MWNOMHW6V3Q4LPDPY4NRW4Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200413%2F5S3MWNOMHW6V3Q4LPDPY4NRW4Y%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=1a096c70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200413%2F5S3MWNOMHW6V3Q4LPDPY4NRW4Y%2F&h=330fc165\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200413/5S3MWNOMHW6V3Q4LPDPY4NRW4Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n泰網紅自稱「台灣女孩」被屈台獨<br />\n<br />\n兩年九個月前的留言，引爆中泰網友的戰火。泰國知名網紅Weetaya（IG賬號nnevvy）早年回覆男友留言「真好看像個中國女孩」時滿頭問號，網民詢問穿着是甚麼風格時，表示為「台灣女孩」風格。此舉觸動中國網民敏感的政治神經，直斥兩人支持「台獨」，要求道歉。泰國網民群起反擊：「武漢肺炎又不見中國道歉？」隨台灣及香港加入網戰，Twitter已出現逾270萬條相關帖文。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200413/large/1586706434_3191.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200413%2Flarge%2F1586706434_3191.gif&h=f5855dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWeetaya一句「台灣女孩」風格引發四地網戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰台港網民圍攻小粉紅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰國劇《因為我們天生一對》（中國譯：假偶天成）廣受中國網民喜愛，男主角Bright知名度急升。不料網民挖出兩年多前他與女友Weetaya的帖文，猛烈狙擊。惟Weetaya「絲毫不理」，其泰國粉絲更直指「那中國為甚麼不為武漢肺炎道歉」，惹來對方強烈反彈。兩國網民炮火越發猛烈，泰網民稱台灣不是中國一部份，也支持香港獨立。中國網民其後怒斥「清邁是個獨立國家」，泰網民完全不介意。中國網民一計不成又來攻擊泰王，嘲泰王在疫情下出逃；不料泰網民早對泰王不滿，只是礙於法例不能斥罵，令中國網民相當無癮。其後台港兩地網民亦加入這場亞洲網民大戰，一同數落中國，熱爆網絡。<br />\n<br />\n著名泰劇繙譯微博專頁「天府泰劇」及「喜翻譯製組」隨後宣佈：「國家面前無大小，字幕組決定即日起停止直播和繙譯，我愛中國！」台灣網民嘲說：「一個盜版網站還敢站出來說話，丟不丟臉。」<br />\n<br />\nTwitter"},{"pid":"a1a9fd64677e0544af63fa7e4efd5df7e736cc94","tid":1970702,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"蕭若元 復活節最佳娛樂節目  中國網民「出征」東南亞勁好笑！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1970930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1970930</a><br />\n<br />\n好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67034d1d708a8e38cf374df2dd4edd3d69d2b024","tid":1970702,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T13:57:57.000Z","msg":"周子瑜事件翻版"},{"pid":"0465f2a98c5c9cc838dd1e71653f810bdf85f657","tid":1970702,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"台灣女孩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNTqrut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNTqrut.jpg&h=c892a33d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d20ecd63388b355b03b1d4e204e11ff58056deb5","tid":1970702,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:01:41.000Z","msg":"其實D 支那人點解可以咁得閒?? 小小事都嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6634dccbef8a1f03895fe019d0b25b00b7340e","tid":1970702,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0465f2a98c5c9cc838dd1e71653f810bdf85f657","tid":1970702,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"台灣女孩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNTqrut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNTqrut.jpg&h=c892a33d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"喂，屌你咩"},{"pid